FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS
- The system must send a confirmation email when a user signs up
- The system must provide to the users the possibility to update their profile information
- The system must provide to the drivers the possibility to publish a new ride
- The system must show the user all the possible journeys according to his needs
- The system must show the user all the information regarding a specific driver
- The system must show to the user the driver, the duration and the cost for a particular ride
- The system must notify the driver when a user asks to change his starting/ending point or the ride cost
- The system must notify the driver when a user asks to join a driver's ride
- The system must notify the user when a driver accepts/rejects his request to join the ride
- The system must notify the driver when a passenger has joined a ride after he has paid
- The system must reject a passenger request if the seats are all occupied
- The system must provide a passenger the possibility to delete a ride booking
- The system must refund a passenger who has deleted a ride if the date of the journey is far away in time (ex max 3 days before)
- The system must provide a driver the possibility to delete a journey
- The system must force a driver who deleted a journey to refund all the passengers if the cancellation date was too close to the journey date (ex max 7 days before)
- The system must ask both the passenger and the driver to leave a review after a ride is ended
- The system must ask the passenger to leave a tip after he has participated in a ride
- The system must block the money a passenger paid until the ride is finished
- The system must ask both passenger and driver if the ride was all good before paying the driver
- The system must send the money to a driver after a passenger has finished the ride and everything was good
- The system must keep blocked the money a passenger paid after the ride has ended if there was a problem during the ride

NON FUNCTIONAL
Product requirements
- The system must satisfy all the user requests in a short time
- The system must encrypt all the sensitive information about passengers, drivers and drivers' cars
Organisational requirements
- (??????)
External Requirements
- The system must be authorized to keep money from passengers before giving them to the driver
- The system must accept only drivers that have an official license and a registered car that doesn't violate any traffic law
- The system must accept only passengers that have an official ID
